arcade.patch.util

Class PatchEnums

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.patch.util.PatchEnums

  • public final class PatchEnums
extends java.lang.Object
    Container class for patch-specific enums.

    Implemented enums include:

    • Ordering defining simulation stepping order
    • State defining cell states
    • Domain defining domain for a given process
    • Flag defining state change flags
    • Category defining operation categories
